Class PhoneBillRestClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.pdx.cs410J.web.HttpRequestHelper
      • edu.pdx.cs410J.whitlock.PhoneBillRestClient

  • public class PhoneBillRestClient
extends HttpRequestHelper
    A helper class for accessing the rest client. Note that this class provides an example of how to make gets and posts to a URL. You'll need to change it to do something other than just send key/value pairs.
